x-6 py-5"><p class="text-sm font-semibold">VMComponent with static id</p><p class="mt-1 text-sm text-demo-muted">This VMComponent renders another VMComponent with a dynamic id inside.</p><code class="mt-3 inline-flex rounded bg-demo-border/40 px-2 py-1 text-xs text-demo-muted">demo-nested-static-vm</code><div class="mt-4"><div class="rounded-xl border border-dashed border-demo-accent/40 bg-demo-card/70 p-4"><p class="text-sm font-semibold">VMComponent with dynamic id</p><p class="mt-1 text-sm text-demo-muted">This nested VMComponent is created without a fixed id.</p><code class="mt-3 inline-flex rounded bg-demo-border/40 px-2 py-1 text-xs text-demo-muted">NestedDemoVM_3_00001</code></div></div></section></div></main>"`;
